flowchart TD
    A[User Login Request] --> B{Credentials Valid?}
    B -->|No| C[401 Unauthorized]
    B -->|Yes| D[Generate Access Token]
    
    D --> E[Sign with Secret Key<br/>HS256]
    E --> F[JWT Created<br/>Header.Payload.Signature]
    
    F --> G[Set Expiry<br/>exp: 15 minutes]
    G --> H[Return to Client]
    
    H --> I[Client Stores Token<br/>Memory / Storage]
    
    I --> J[Client Makes API Request<br/>Authorization: Bearer token]
    
    J --> K{Token Verification}
    K -->|Invalid Signature| L[401 Invalid Token]
    K -->|Expired| M[401 Token Expired]
    K -->|Valid| N[Decode Payload]
    
    N --> O[Extract userId, username]
    O --> P[Process Request]
    P --> Q[Return Response]
